OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1770626963
OL,3,C'I was exploited', says woman who
OL,4,Cworked for politician illegally
OL,6,F"This case was never simply about
OL,7,Flegal thresholds. It was about what
OL,8,Fhappens when power goes unchecked,
OL,9,Fvulnerability is ignored, and
OL,10,Fsafeguarding fails in practice.
OL,12,F"A community service sentence does not
OL,13,Ferase the human cost of that failure."
OL,15,FShe said: "There are lessons here
OL,16,Fabout how migrant workers are treated
OL,17,Fand how harm can be minimised by
OL,18,Fprocess. I will continue to speak not
OL,19,Fin anger, but in truth because
OL,20,Faccountability does not begin or end
OL,21,Fin a courtroom."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
