OL,3,C'I was exploited', says woman who
OL,4,Cworked for politician illegally
OL,6,FLiliane, who has returned home to
OL,7,FRwanda, says she hopes to come back to
OL,8,FJersey one day.
OL,10,FFollowing the sentencing, political
OL,11,Fparty Reform Jersey issued a statement
OL,12,Fquestioning whether Ozouf should
OL,13,Fcontinue in his role has a States
OL,14,Fmember.
OL,16,FIt said: "All migrant workers who come
OL,17,Fto Jersey to live and work deserve to
OL,18,Fbe treated with dignity and respect,
OL,19,Fand should be protected from
OL,20,Fexploitation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
