OL,3,C'I was exploited', says woman who
OL,4,Cworked for politician illegally
OL,6,F"Elected representatives are rightly
OL,7,Fheld to the highest standards of
OL,8,Fconduct, and the public must be able
OL,9,Fto trust that those entrusted with
OL,10,Fmaking the law will themselves respect
OL,11,Fit."
OL,13,F"This case raises important questions
OL,14,Fabout accountability, and about the
OL,15,Fmessage sent to migrant workers and to
OL,16,Fthe wider community if those standards
OL,17,Fare seen to be compromised."
